
########################
Create GSM and GSE plots
########################

Create_plots.idl    --- idl calling script. set the environment for the plot

cheph_gsm.pro           ---  crate GSE.gif and GSM.gif
                        data needed:   /data/mta4/Space_Weather/ephem/Data/PE.EPH.gsme
                                    /data/mta4/Space_Weather/ephem/Data/dsn_summary.dat
                                    /data/mta4/Space_Weather/CRM/Data/CRM_p.dat30

                        output:         <plot_dir>/GSM.gif <plot_dir>/GSE.gif
                            where:
                            <plot_dir>: /data/mta4/www/RADIATION_new/Orbit/Plots/



################################
Creating GSE/GSM 3D orbit plots
################################

extract_next_two_days.py    --- extract two days amount of data from /proj/rac/ops/ephem/PE.EPH.gsme_in_Re

gsm_plots.idl               --- controlling script, calling gsm_plots.pro
gsm_plots.pro               --- main idl script to create GSEORBIT.gif and GSMORBIT.gif
read_ephemeris.pro          --- collection of idl functions used by gsm_plots
Template/FluxImageColorKey.gif  --- color code list

Input:
<ephem_dir>/Data/PE.EPH.gsme_in_Re

output:
    <data_dir>/gs_data_2_day

Input:
    <data_dir>/gs_data_2_day

Output:
    /data/mta4/www/RADIATION_new/Orbit/Plots/GSEORBIT.gif
    /data/mta4/www/RADIATION_new/Orbit/Plots/GSMORBIT.gif

web page:
    cxc.cfa.harvard.edu/mta/RADIATION_new/Orbit/orbit.html (top two plots)


cronjob:
--------
han-v as mta

12,32,52 *  * * * cd /data/mta4/Space_Weather/GSM_plots/Scripts/; /usr/local/bin/idl Create_plots.idl > /data/mta4/Space_Weather/Test_Logs/gsm_create_plot.cron 2>&1
10 8,20     * * * /data/mta4/Space_Weather/GSM_plots/Scripts/gsm_wrap_script                          > /data/mta4/Space_Weather/Test_Logs/gsm_extract_gsm_data.cron 2>&1
15 8,20     * * * cd /data/mta4/Space_Weather/GSM_plots/Scripts/; /usr/local/bin/idl  gsm_plots.idl   > /data/mta4/Space_Weather/Test_Logs/gsm_3c_gsm_plot.cron 2>&1


